ActMigratory Birds Convention Act, 1994
SubjectRegulations Amending the Migratory Birds Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the MIGRATORY BIRDS REGULATIONS, in order to change hunting season dates for certain species for the 2011/2012 hunting season and to set daily bag limits and possession limits for migratory game birds. The amendments include special conservation measures for overabundant snow geese populations.
